snippet.title: Rooftops Classic Full Mod
snippet.description:
Rooftops Campaign Classic is a Call of Duty 4 Custom Singleplayer Campaign that came out in 2016.
A huge revamp of this mod is upcoming in a few months which will remaster the mod.
